text: Dominique Swain (born August 12 1980 in Malibu, California) is an American actress. She has been in many movies. She is best known for her role as the title character in the 1997 drama Lolita. Swain also played Jamie Archer in the movie Face/Off. ==References== Category:Actors from Malibu, California Category:American movie actors Category:1980 births Category:Living people
